18
00:01:12,310 --> 00:01:12,870
Fine.

19
00:01:13,510 --> 00:01:14,150
Fine.

20
00:01:14,790 --> 00:01:15,480
Xiao Lang.

21
00:01:15,950 --> 00:01:16,640
Mr. Xiao.

22
00:01:17,070 --> 00:01:17,760
Mr. Xiao!

23
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,310
I'm sorry.

24
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:20,710
I was wrong.

25
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,120
Forgive me.

26
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,710
Su Mingyu!

27
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,710
