36
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:03,640
Zixing,

37
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:04,920
I'm sorry.

38
00:02:05,310 --> 00:02:07,560
I never knew my father worked with Gao Rui

39
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,120
