40
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,150
And yet I helped them,

41
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:13,680
letting them hurt you even more.

42
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:14,730
You...

43
00:02:15,150 --> 00:02:16,000
