59
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,910
If I had been by your side,

60
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:56,280
you wouldn't have been so lonely

61
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,960
or so cold.

62
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,190
I'm sorry.

63
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,190
Yu,

64
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,400
