73
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:53,510
I'll get you some medicine.

74
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,720
I don't want medicine.

75
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,000
It's too bitter.

76
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,510
But you'll get sick like this.

77
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,920
I want something sweet.

78
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:18,770
