79
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:20,070
weren't sweet at all.

80
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:21,920
That was a lie.

81
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,830
I'm heading to work.

82
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,800
We're already at the company.

83
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:57,120
