87
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,040
What distance?

88
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,870
I can't keep my distance from my girlfriend.

89
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,560
You should focus on work

90
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:17,870
and do whatever you want to do.

91
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,870
You should stay away from Li Ziyang.

92
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,070
Don't worry.

93
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,040
I'm going.

94
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,600
Go on.

95
00:06:42,430 --> 00:06:43,070
Madam Man,

96
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:44,800
