99
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:56,680
But Su Mingyu really isn't at fault.

100
00:06:56,950 --> 00:06:58,000
She never hurt me

101
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,190
or my mother.

102
00:07:00,270 --> 00:07:01,270
For my sake,

103
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,270
could you stop rejecting her so much?

104
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,160
During those two years

105
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,190
when my mother was imprisoned and you were cast out,

106
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:17,040
Yu was the one

107
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:19,720
who helped me through my darkest days.

108
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:21,870
When I was locked up,

109
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:22,920
she set me free.

110
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:24,270
When I was injured,

111
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:25,240
she took care of me.

112
00:07:25,630 --> 00:07:27,430
She doesn't know what her father did,

113
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,630
but she waited for me

114
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,600
for eighteen long years.

115
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:37,430
Yu is the only light I have left.

116
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:40,070
Madam Man,

117
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:42,560
